title: GOP governor calls MTG's rhetoric 'evil'
description: Gov. Spencer Cox (R-UT) fired back at Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene's (R-GA) calls for a "national divorce" Monday, calling the idea "evil."

title: Whitmer kidnapping trial advances
description: (The Center Square) – More than two years after the alleged plot to kidnap Gov. Gretchen Whitmer was foiled, criminal cases against alleged perpetrators are still working their way through the court system.
